snippet.title: Japan: Johnny Depp and fiancee Amber Heard greet fans in Tokyo
snippet.description:
Hollywood actor Johnny Depp and his actress and model fiancee, Amber Heard, arrived at Haneda airport in Tokyo, Monday. The two are attending the film showing of his new film Mortdecai, which is scheduled to take place on Tuesday.
